prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom White Racer Blue
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/High/Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom White Racer Blue
prod.desciption:
Jordan Brand revamped a classic silhouette with the release of the Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom White Racer Blue, now available on StockX. Nike Zoom technology is incorporated in this design for the ultimate cushioning experience.

This Jordan 1 Retro High consists of a white leather upper with a mixture of mesh, patent leather, and translucent TPU overlays. An icy outsole, blue interior, and Zoom branding above the Swoosh completes the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $175.
